gujarati.context:
Here is the translation:

For you I will take the initiative, say I will make harmony with you; 
Become pleased and accept, then it will remain as a sweet melody.

Here is the translation:

Saying this, they reached their village; 
With good company, they went with Saint Sujan.

Here is the translation:

That place has been celebrated, spring's sweet delight; 
When seen in imagination, my heart became entwined with it.

Here is the translation:

He was a good son, on the great fifth day of the month; 
In Dharmapur, Kusalkumar, there he did playful life.
